  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nPresently we are not using the bulk signature verification method. This has previously shown a 30% decrease in verification times.\r\n\r\nThe `VerifyBulk` strategy is what we want:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/e7de1b3339818614b209049bc1bbdb4622aef06f/eth2/state_processing/src/per_block_processing.rs#L35-L44\r\n\r\n## To resolve\r\n\r\n- Ensure all the EF tests are running with `VerifyBulk`\r\n- Change the strategy in `BeaconChain::process_block_internal` (see below)\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/e7de1b3339818614b209049bc1bbdb4622aef06f/beacon_node/beacon_chain/src/beacon_chain.rs#L1268-L1282\r\n",
